{"about_the_game":"<strong>Fungiman is an atmospheric and challenging first person survival horror game.</strong><br><br>You find yourself in the forest, as in fifty thousand billion other games. You admire nature, beautiful flowers, trees and mineshafts and do not even suspect that &quot;He&quot;, the warden of the Fungar forest, the F\u00fcngiman, has been watching you all this time.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006330/extras/fungif.gif?t=1733610994\" /><br><br>Why is he following you? He makes sure that no one touches his donuts \u2014 the main source of his f\u00fcngus power. But you also need these donuts, simply because you are a human, and these donuts are <i><strong>really</strong></i> delicious. And you want to collect and eat them all.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006330/extras/fungiftoo.gif?t=1733610994\" /><br><br>It would seem that the F\u00fcngus will be angry if you eat his donuts... <strong>or not?</strong><br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br>\u2022 F\u00fcngiman changes his behavior and tactics throughout the game<br>\u2022 Two levels: classic and reworked<br>\u2022 Diverse locations<br>\u2022 Secret minigames<br>\u2022 Multiplayer","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Heartless","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2006330/501b3dedd80abb633e14ac373f033c04c778b3ce.jpg"},{"name":"Was it worth it?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2006330/ba1b62e7fa93f9113cee4c788dca34f88905ee64.jpg"},{"name":"UFO","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2006330/32b451f34dbb43bc36cd98d9b2dae43a54a4c989.jpg"},{"name":"Clumsy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2006330/92f90d446f403eb182efa837f7fdec1e37536e09.jpg"},{"name":"Spa session","path":"https://c